The evidence with the title 'Fake Walt Disney world pages on facebook trick thousands of users ' says Mar 19, 2014  ... The following message is posted on them every few hours :  ... Win an all paid for Florida , Disney World vacation with passes to every park .  ... Each of the scam Walt Disney World pages has been liked by thousands of users .  ... These like- farming scams have been making the rounds for quite some time now . 
